comments: Mitchell (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position on George (LAC) during the drive, and the contact is incidental.
George (LAC) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two legal steps.
George (LAC) briefly places his arm to Mitchell's (UTA) front and does not affect his SQBR at the start of his drive.
Batum (LAC) makes contact with Mitchell's (UTA) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) makes marginal contact to Leonard's (LAC) off-arm during his driving shot attempt.
George (LAC) makes incidental contact with Mitchell (UTA) as he attempts to cut towards the basket off-ball.
Bogdanovic (UTA) makes incidental contact to Morris Sr.'s (LAC) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) commits a take foul on Leonard (LAC).
Mitchell (UTA) cleanly deflects the inbounds pass to George (LAC).
George (LAC) makes incidental contact to Mitchell's (UTA) upper body during his dribble in the backcourt.
Mitchell (UTA) deflects the ball away from George (LAC) during his dribble.
George (LAC) makes contact to Bogdanovic's (UTA) arm and affects his SQBR after recovering the loose ball.
Mitchell (UTA) makes clean contact to the ball while defending the inbounds pass to Leonard (LAC).
Mitchell (UTA) commits a take foul on Beverley (LAC).
Bogdanovic (UTA) commits a take foul on Leonard (LAC).
Morris Sr. (LAC) legally contests Mitchell (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Mitchell (UTA) commits a take foul on Beverley (LAC).
The crew communicated with the Replay Center Official who determined that a common foul would be assessed.
There is no conclusive angle to determine whether Mitchell's (UTA) right heel makes contact with the sideline.
There is no conclusive angle to determine whether Beverley (LAC) makes clean contact with the ball or Mitchell's (UTA) arm during the jump shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (UTA) commits a take foul on Leonard (LAC).
George (LAC) reaches in and makes contact to Mitchell's (UTA) left arm at the end of his drive, and the contact occurs prior to his upward shooting motion.
Mitchell (UTA) enters the lane prior to the ball hitting the rim.
